metadata.name: Land On Spacetime #1
metadata.description: The Land On Spacetime is a collection of 10000 rare NFTs residing on the Ethereum Blockchain about space events & projects that will happen in the future. The collection contains 10000 extraordinary handmade date layers starting from 01/01/2022 & ending on 26/05/2049, along with more than 400 rarities. So, each NFT includes a real time on Blockchain. Therefore, holders will benefit from having a specific time on Blockchain, granting access to members-only benefits & priority access to space travel in the future. Future perks & benefits for members will be unlocked by the community through the roadmap.
metadata.creator: Land On Spacetime Club
